@startuml
actor User
participant "Web Application\n(Streamlit)" as WebApp
participant "Azure OpenAI Service" as OpenAI
participant "Vector Store\n(Azure Cognitive Search/Redis/PGVector)" as VectorStore
participant "GPT-3" as GPT3
participant "Azure Function\n(BatchStartProcessing)" as BatchStart
participant "Azure Queue" as Queue
participant "Azure Function\n(BatchPushResults)" as BatchProcess
participant "Azure Blob Storage" as BlobStorage

User -> WebApp: Ask question
WebApp -> OpenAI: Create query embedding
OpenAI --> WebApp: Return query embedding
WebApp -> VectorStore: Search similar document chunks
VectorStore --> WebApp: Return relevant chunks
WebApp -> GPT3: Generate answer (query + chunks)
GPT3 --> WebApp: Return generated answer
WebApp --> User: Display answer

User -> WebApp: Upload documents
WebApp -> BatchStart: Trigger batch processing
BatchStart -> Queue: Add processing messages
Queue --> BatchProcess: Trigger processing
BatchProcess -> BlobStorage: Read document files
BlobStorage --> BatchProcess: Return file content
BatchProcess -> OpenAI: Create document embeddings
OpenAI --> BatchProcess: Return embeddings
BatchProcess -> VectorStore: Store document embeddings
@enduml